    <graphic url="https://iiif.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/iiif/image/988dc873-497b-4df5-94a6-f1f438a69643"/>
    <zone type="main">
        <line>When cities sink howling in ruin, &amp; ye</line>
        <line>Who with wingless footsteps trample the Sea</line>
        <line>And close upon Shipwreck &amp; Famines track</line>
        <line>Sit chattering with joy on the foodless wreck</line>
        <line rend="center">Come, Come, Come!</line>
        <line rend="indent1">Leave the bed, low cold &amp; red</line>
        <line rend="indent1">Strewed beneath a nation dead;</line>
        <line rend="indent1">Leave the hatred— as in ashes</line> 
        <line rend="indent1">Fire is left for future burning,—</line>
        <line rend="indent1">It will burst in bloodier flashes</line>
        <line rend="indent1">When ye stir it soon returning;</line>
        <line rend="indent1">Leave the self contempt implanted</line>
        <line rend="indent1">In young spirits sense-<mod><del rend="overwritten">i</del><add place="intralinear">e</add></mod>nchanted</line>
        <line rend="indent1">Misery's yet unkindled fuel;</line>
        <line rend="indent1"><mod><del rend="strikethrough">He</del> <add place="intralinear">Leave<del rend="strikethrough">s</del></add></mod>
            Hells' secrets half-uncharted</line>
        <line rend="indent2">To the maniac dreamer: cruel</line>
        <line rend="indent3">More than ye can be with hate,</line>
        <line rend="indent4">Is he with fear.</line>
        <line rend="indent4">Come, Come come!</line>
        <line>We are steaming up from Hells wide <add place="superlinear">gate</add></line>
    </zone>
</surface>
